"parikkhayaṃ gacchanti, mohadhammā vā parikkhayaṃ gacchanti."
msgstr ""
"‘It’s not because of one’s extremely wealthy family that thoughts of greed, "
"hate, or delusion come to an end."

msgctxt "mn113:4-6.10"
msgid "No cepi uḷārabhogakulā pabbajito hoti;"
msgstr "Even if someone has not gone forth from an extremely wealthy family,"

msgctxt "mn113:4-6.11"
msgid ""
