"tattha pujjo, so tattha pāsaṃso’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn113:14.10"
msgid ""
"So paṭipadaṃyeva antaraṃ karitvā tena piṇḍapātikattena nevattānukkaṃseti, na "
"paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn113:14.11"
msgid "Ayampi, bhikkhave, sappurisadhammo. (12)"
msgstr ""

