#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya16-20"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "mn113:16-20.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, asappuriso sosāniko hoti … pe …"
msgstr "who stays in a charnel ground …"

msgctxt "mn113:16-20.2"
msgid "abbhokāsiko hoti …"
msgstr "who stays in the open air …"

msgctxt "mn113:16-20.3"
msgid "nesajjiko hoti … pe …"
msgstr "who never lies down …"

msgctxt "mn113:16-20.4"
msgid "yathāsanthatiko hoti … pe …"
msgstr "who sleeps wherever they lay their mat ..."

msgctxt "mn113:16-20.5"
msgid "ekāsaniko hoti."
msgstr "who eats in one sitting per day."

msgctxt "mn113:16-20.6"
msgid "So iti paṭisañcikkhati:"
msgstr "They reflect:"

msgctxt "mn113:16-20.7"
msgid "‘ahaṃ khomhi ekāsaniko, ime panaññe bhikkhū na ekāsanikā’ti."
msgstr "‘I eat in one sitting per day, unlike these other mendicants.’"

msgctxt "mn113:16-20.8"
msgid "So tena ekāsanikattena attānukkaṃseti, paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr "And they glorify themselves and put others down on account of that."

msgctxt "mn113:16-20.9"
msgid "Ayampi, bhikkhave, asappurisadhammo."
msgstr "This too is a quality of a bad person."

msgctxt "mn113:16-20.10"
msgid "Sappuriso ca kho, bhikkhave, iti paṭisañcikkhati:"
msgstr "A good person reflects:"

msgctxt "mn113:16-20.11"
msgid ""
"‘na kho ekāsanikattena lobhadhammā vā parikkhayaṃ gacchanti, dosadhammā vā "
"parikkhayaṃ gacchanti, mohadhammā vā parikkhayaṃ gacchanti."
msgstr ""
"‘It’s not because of eating in one sitting per day that thoughts of greed, "
"hate, or delusion come to an end."

msgctxt "mn113:16-20.12"
msgid "No cepi ekāsaniko hoti;"
msgstr "Even if someone eats in more than one sitting per day,"

msgctxt "mn113:16-20.13"
msgid ""
"so ca hoti dhammānudhammappaṭipanno sāmīcippaṭipanno anudhammacārī, so "
"tattha pujjo, so tattha pāsaṃso’ti."
msgstr ""
"if they practice in line with the teaching, practice properly, and live in "
"line with the teaching, they are worthy of honor and praise for that.’"

msgctxt "mn113:16-20.14"
msgid ""
"So paṭipadaṃyeva antaraṃ karitvā tena ekāsanikattena nevattānukkaṃseti, na "
"paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr ""
"Keeping only the practice close to their heart, they don’t glorify "
"themselves and put others down on account of their eating in one sitting per "
"day."

msgctxt "mn113:16-20.15"
msgid "Ayampi, bhikkhave, sappurisadhammo. (14–18.)"
msgstr "This too is a quality of a good person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya21"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.43"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "mn113:21.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, asappuriso vivicceva kāmehi vivicca akusalehi "
"dhammehi savitakkaṃ savicāraṃ vivekajaṃ pītisukhaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ "
"upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, take a bad person who, quite secluded from sensual pleasures, "
"secluded from unskillful qualities, enters and remains in the first "
"absorption, which has the rapture and bliss born of seclusion, while placing "
"the mind and keeping it connected."

msgctxt "mn113:21.2"
msgid "So iti paṭisañcikkhati:"
msgstr "They reflect:"

msgctxt "mn113:21.3"
msgid ""
"‘ahaṃ khomhi paṭhamajjhānasamāpattiyā lābhī, ime panaññe bhikkhū "
"paṭhamajjhānasamāpattiyā na lābhino’ti."
msgstr "‘I have attained the first absorption, unlike these other mendicants.’"

msgctxt "mn113:21.4"
msgid "So tāya paṭhamajjhānasamāpattiyā attānukkaṃseti, paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr "And they glorify themselves and put others down on account of that."

msgctxt "mn113:21.5"
msgid "Ayampi, bhikkhave, asappurisadhammo."
msgstr "This too is a quality of a bad person."

msgctxt "mn113:21.6"
msgid "Sappuriso ca kho, bhikkhave, iti paṭisañcikkhati:"
msgstr "A good person reflects:"

msgctxt "mn113:21.7"
msgid "‘paṭhamajjhānasamāpattiyāpi kho atammayatā vuttā bhagavatā."
msgstr ""
"‘The Buddha has spoken of not identifying even with the attainment of the "
"first absorption."

msgctxt "mn113:21.8"
msgid "Yena yena hi maññanti tato taṃ hoti aññathā’ti."
msgstr "For however they conceive it, it turns out to be something else.’"

msgctxt "mn113:21.9"
msgid ""
"So atammayataññeva antaraṃ karitvā tāya paṭhamajjhānasamāpattiyā "
"nevattānukkaṃseti, na paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr ""
"Keeping only non-identification close to their heart, they don’t glorify "
"themselves and put others down on account of their attainment of the first "
"absorption."

msgctxt "mn113:21.10"
msgid "Ayampi, bhikkhave, sappurisadhammo. (19)"
msgstr "This too is a quality of a good person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya22-24"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "mn113:22-24.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, asappuriso vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā ajjhattaṃ "
"sampasādanaṃ cetaso ekodibhāvaṃ avitakkaṃ avicāraṃ samādhijaṃ pītisukhaṃ "
"dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, take a bad person who, as the placing of the mind and keeping "
"it connected are stilled, enters and remains in the second absorption …"

msgctxt "mn113:22-24.2"
msgid "tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ …"
msgstr "third absorption …"

msgctxt "mn113:22-24.3"
msgid "catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr "fourth absorption."

msgctxt "mn113:22-24.4"
msgid "So iti paṭisañcikkhati:"
msgstr "They reflect:"

msgctxt "mn113:22-24.5"
msgid ""
"‘ahaṃ khomhi catutthajjhānasamāpattiyā lābhī, ime panaññe bhikkhū "
"catutthajjhānasamāpattiyā na lābhino’ti."
msgstr "‘I have attained the fourth absorption, unlike these other mendicants.’"

msgctxt "mn113:22-24.6"
msgid "So tāya catutthajjhānasamāpattiyā attānukkaṃseti, paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr "And they glorify themselves and put others down on account of that."

msgctxt "mn113:22-24.7"
msgid "Ayampi, bhikkhave, asappurisadhammo."
msgstr "This too is a quality of a bad person."

msgctxt "mn113:22-24.8"
msgid "Sappuriso ca kho, bhikkhave, iti paṭisañcikkhati:"
msgstr "A good person reflects:"

msgctxt "mn113:22-24.9"
msgid "‘catutthajjhānasamāpattiyāpi kho atammayatā vuttā bhagavatā."
msgstr ""
"‘The Buddha has spoken of not identifying even with the attainment of the "
"fourth absorption."

msgctxt "mn113:22-24.10"
msgid "Yena yena hi maññanti tato taṃ hoti aññathā’ti."
msgstr "For however they conceive it, it turns out to be something else.’"

msgctxt "mn113:22-24.11"
msgid ""
"So atammayataññeva antaraṃ karitvā tāya catutthajjhānasamāpattiyā "
"nevattānukkaṃseti, na paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr ""
"Keeping only non-identification close to their heart, they don’t glorify "
"themselves and put others down on account of their attainment of the fourth "
"absorption."

msgctxt "mn113:22-24.12"
msgid "Ayampi, bhikkhave, sappurisadhammo. (20–22.)"
msgstr "This too is a quality of a good person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya25"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "mn113:25.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, asappuriso sabbaso rūpasaññānaṃ samatikkamā "
"paṭighasaññānaṃ atthaṅgamā nānattasaññānaṃ amanasikārā ‘ananto ākāso’ti "
"ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, take someone who, going totally beyond perceptions of form, "
"with the ending of perceptions of impingement, not focusing on perceptions "
"of diversity, aware that ‘space is infinite’, enters and remains in the "
"dimension of infinite space …"

msgctxt "mn113:25.2"
msgid "So iti paṭisañcikkhati:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn113:25.3"
msgid ""
"‘ahaṃ khomhi ākāsānañcāyatanasamāpattiyā lābhī, ime panaññe bhikkhū "
"ākāsānañcāyatanasamāpattiyā na lābhino’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn113:25.4"
msgid "So tāya ākāsānañcāyatanasamāpattiyā attānukkaṃseti, paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn113:25.5"
msgid "Ayampi, bhikkhave, asappurisadhammo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn113:25.6"
msgid "Sappuriso ca kho, bhikkhave, iti paṭisañcikkhati:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn113:25.7"
msgid "‘ākāsānañcāyatanasamāpattiyāpi kho atammayatā vuttā bhagavatā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn113:25.8"
msgid "Yena yena hi maññanti tato taṃ hoti aññathā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn113:25.9"
msgid ""
"So atammayataññeva antaraṃ karitvā tāya ākāsānañcāyatanasamāpattiyā "
"nevattānukkaṃseti, na paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn113:25.10"
msgid "Ayampi, bhikkhave, sappurisadhammo. (23)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya26"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.44"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
